4
0:00:26.638,000 --> 0:00:29,000
about the person you were delivering.

5
0:00:31.864,000 --> 0:00:34,000
And you can all mouth it if you want or say it out loud.

6
0:00:35.729,000 --> 0:00:4,000
It was -- the first two were, "It's a ..."

7
0:00:41.31,000 --> 0:00:43,000
Audience: (Mixed reply) Girl. Boy.

8
0:00:43.355,000 --> 0:00:44,000
