195
0:11:27.18,000 --> 0:11:29,000
Did they come from Afghanistan? No.

196
0:11:30.44,000 --> 0:11:37,000
75 percent of them came from within 150 miles of Boston.

197
0:11:38.701,000 --> 0:11:4,000
And some came from England.

198
0:11:42.138,000 --> 0:11:46,000
